message.content: cs.LO, cs.LO is the most likely category as the paper deals with logic and its semantics. Other likely categories could be cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) as the paper deals with endofunctors and functors, cs.CC (Computational Complexity) as the paper discusses the complexity of computing posetifications and positivications, cs.PL (Programming Languages) as the paper deals with syntax-building functors, and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper discusses modal logics which are often used in AI.
